class Solution(object):
    def minOperations(self, nums, k):
        """
        :type nums: List[int]
        :type k: int
        :rtype: int
        """
        target_set = set(range(1, k + 1))
        collected_set = set()
        operations = 0

        while target_set != collected_set:
            element = nums.pop()
            collected_set.add(element)
            operations += 1

        return operations
